To run this application the user should have node.js,mongodb connectivity.
Install node.js in your system.
Open the terminal and cd into the project folder and install the required dependancies used in the app.js.(Eg:express,mongoose,mongodb,lodash,ejs,body-parser.etc.,).
Run node app.js 
The server would start on port 3000.
In the web browser by typing localhost:3000 the application is opened.
